{"id":237963,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/网爆人民日报记者欲报天津大火遭阻（附报道原文/","date":"2012-07-06T00:37:43Z","modified":"2012-07-06T01:01:57Z","title":"网曝人民日报记者欲报天津大火遭阻（附报道原文）","content":"<p>6月30日的天津蓟县商场大火发生之后，官方报道的10死16伤的说法<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B0%91%E8%AE%AE-%E9%81%BF%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B4%A5%E6%88%90%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6/\">遭到大量网民的质疑</a>，更有不少天津市民自发统计伤亡人数。同时，天津市还禁止外地记者入津采访，引起不少网民大呼“天津要独立了”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin4.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-237964\" title=\"tianjin4\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"568\" height=\"810\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin4.png 568w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin4-210x300.png 210w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 568px) 100vw, 568px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-237965\" title=\"tianjin3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"566\" height=\"503\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin3.jpg 566w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin3-300x266.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin_人民日报.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-237967\" title=\"tianjin_人民日报\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin_人民日报.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"435\" height=\"841\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin_人民日报.jpg 435w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/tianjin_人民日报-155x300.jpg 155w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 435px) 100vw, 435px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,205